{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I forgot to mention, to give a-- gave a concession, like a permit, to open for all the businesspeople together for one store.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So in the beginning, for a short time, they allow it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And also before it, this, we got this big-- this concession allowed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had-- my daddy knew someone also from business, Gentile, who they wanted to get together, because my daddy spoke fluently German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they went to buy in transaction to make some time German people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they-- they bought some cattle for $10,000.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So my daddy who went with him and they made the transaction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I don't know if they put deposit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "One day, they promised, if they come back, they get whatever they bought.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The cattle.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then when Daddy came back, they took the money and beat him up and never got anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we didn't know what happened to Daddy for couple days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We couldn't show up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was-- obviously he was unable to come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that started-- the situation started to get very drastic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that time when-- that was after that, that my daddy decided to take, after he got strong and better, he got-- took my brother and tried to save him from-- they started already talking about concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was all kind of rumors, which they did not tell us, but like we could see that something is going on very serious.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that's why Daddy took him, my brother, to Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Russia was-- actually that wasn't Russia, belonged to Poland, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that's how he met my sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He was 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My sister-in-law was 19, but he looked much more mature.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She said she would never have married somebody her age, have to be six, seven years older.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
